{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0bfd6c5f88","title":"关于出版三十本马、恩、列、斯著作的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c6a1e385b0","index":0,"year":1964,"month":2,"day":13,"articleId":"0bfd6c5f88"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d08502bc95","type":"title","text":"关于出版三十本马、恩、列、斯著作的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"0bfd6c5f88"},{"id":"09afcd7807","type":"paragraph","text":"×××同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"0bfd6c5f88"},{"id":"252d91a621","type":"paragraph","text":"一、此件看过，很好，可以立即发下去。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"0bfd6c5f88"},{"id":"ebdaa4c8f7","type":"paragraph","text":"二、三十本书，大字线装，分册（一部大书分十册、八册，小书不分册，中书仍要分册），请你督促迅速办下去。希望今年办成，可以吗？你想一下告我为盼。每部印一万、两万分，好吗？我急于想要看这种大字书。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"0bfd6c5f88"}],"page":{"id":"501b2a8e68","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"0bfd6c5f88","start":183,"end":183}}}},"__N_SSG":true}